    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、{user}さんですか\nちゃんと前を見て歩いていただかなければ、困ります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ {user}-san.\nYou should watch where you're going.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.4035147508,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いや、それは俺の台詞……もしかして\nまたコンタクト落として、前が見えてなかったんですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ that's my line… oh wait‚\ndid you lose your contact lens again and couldn't see?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 24.4570288499
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "人を年がら年中、コンタクトを落とす\n間抜けのように言わないで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't treat me like a fool\nwho lose contact lens all year round.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 28.8836955547
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "今はちゃんと装着しています。ですからさっき\n{user}さんと呼んだじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm wearing them properly now. That's why\nI correctly called you \"{user}-san\"‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.0358953953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　……あ、確かに\nいやぁ、mihoさんがまたぶつかってるからてっきり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!? …Oh‚ right.\nWell‚ you bumped into me again‚ so I just assumed…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 41.790727218
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "貴方が、私を大間抜けと思っていることは\nよく分かりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now I understand very well that you think\nI’m a complete fool.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.0832216104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 46.8223601342
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "その忌々しい認識は後で話し合うこととして……\nそれで、クリスマスライブの相談とはなんなんです？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's talk later about that annoying recognition…\nSo‚ what did you want to discuss about regarding the Christmas live?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.1832216104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう、スケジュールが変更になりまして\nライブのリハ、スリクスは木曜に回させてくれと連絡が",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh yes‚ there's been a change in the schedule.\nThey've asked if we can move IIIX's rehearsal to Thursday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.4999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 62.882449468
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "……分かりました。年末の急なスケジュール変更は\n毎年のことですし、仕方ないですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I understand. Sudden schedule changes at the end of the year\nare an annual occurrence. It can't be helped.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.8833108108,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "……それに、忙しい方が気が紛れていいですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Besides‚ it's better to be busy to distract myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.0931733132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 71.0931733132
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 75.5760306041
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "さっきも随分、ぼうっとしてらっしゃいましたけど\nもしかして、何か悩み事でも………………あ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seemed pretty spaced out earlier‚\ndo you have any concerns… ah‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.5666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……もうすぐ、クリスマスですもんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Christmas is just around the corner.",
