    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "死んでからもしばらく一緒にいたから、墓参りってのも\nなんだか変な気分だよな。なあ、麻奈",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It feels strange visiting your grave since we spent time together for a while\neven after you died. Mana‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.5333221435,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s5",
      "startTime": 125.4333343506
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃も、俺達も、あれからもなんとかやってる……\n……ダメだな、話したいことは沢山あるんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono‚ and all of us‚ are doing okay… somehow…\n…I'm bad at this. I have so much I want to say‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.6851892632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_05_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "いざ話そうとすると、まとまらないもんだな\n……それじゃ、仕事に行ってくるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but I can't put it into words.\n…Alright then‚ I will go to work.",
        "id": ""
      },
